HEADWORD: Royal spade
<hw>Royal spade</hw>. <fld>(Auction Bridge)</fld> <def>A spade when
spades are trumps under the condition that every trick over six taken by
the successful bidder has a score value of 9; -- usually in
<pluf>pl.</pluf></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

